                <p>
                  ʾAbbā Jeremiah was an Egyptian monk. Several texts
                  (amongst them, the <title ref="LIT1239Chroni">Chronicle of John of Nikiu</title>)
                  attest his connection to the emperor
                  <persName ref="PRS1908Anastasi">Anastasius</persName> (491-518) and to the 
                  city of <placeName ref="LOC4764Memphi">Memphis</placeName>.
                </p>
